### Test Order Processing System APIs

### 1. Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "fullName": "Test User"
}

### 2. Login to get JWT token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Create a category (Admin required)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Đặc sản miền Bắc",
  "description": "Các sản phẩm đặc sản từ miền Bắc Việt Nam"
}

### 4. Create a product (Admin required)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Bánh chưng Hà Nội",
  "description": "Bánh chưng truyền thống Hà Nội, làm từ gạo nếp, đậu xanh và thịt heo",
  "price": 150000,
  "stockQuantity": 50,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "isActive": true,
  "isFeatured": true,
  "weightGrams": 500,
  "origin": "Hà Nội"
}

### 5. Add product to cart
POST http://localhost:8080/api/cart/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}

### 6. View cart
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 7. Create shipping address
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/addresses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "fullName": "Test User",
  "phoneNumber": "0123456789",
  "addressLine1": "123 Đường ABC",
  "city": "Hà Nội",
  "province": "Hà Nội",
  "postalCode": "100000",
  "country": "Vietnam",
  "isDefault": true
}

### 8. Create order from cart
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "shippingAddressId": 1,
  "paymentMethod": "Credit Card",
  "notes": "Giao hàng vào buổi sáng"
}

### 9. Get user's orders
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/my-orders
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 10. Get order by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 11. Update order status (Admin only)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/orders/admin/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "status": "CONFIRMED",
  "notes": "Đơn hàng đã được xác nhận"
}

### 12. Get inventory statistics (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/statistics
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 13. Get low stock products (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/low-stock
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 14. Update product stock (Admin only)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/products/1/stock?quantity=100
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 15. Cancel order
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 16. Search orders (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/admin/search?searchTerm=test
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 17. Get order statistics (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/admin/statistics
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE